<rss version="2.0"><channel><title>GitHub Trending: Smarty, This week</title><link>https://github.com/trending/smarty?since=weekly</link><description>The top repositories on GitHub for smarty, measured weekly</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2019 01:06:05 GMT</pubDate><lastBuildDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2019 01:06:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>PyRSS2Gen-1.1.0</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><ttl>720</ttl><item><title>confluentinc/cp-helm-charts #1 in Smarty, This week</title><link>https://github.com/confluentinc/cp-helm-charts</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;The Confluent Platform Helm charts enable you to deploy Confluent Platform services on Kubernetes for development, test, and proof of concept environments.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id="readme" class="instapaper_body md" data-path="README.md"&gt;&lt;article class="markdown-body entry-content p-5" itemprop="text"&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-confluent-open-source-helm-chart" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#confluent-open-source-helm-chart"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Confluent Open Source Helm Chart&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Confluent Platform Helm charts are in developer preview and are not supported for production use.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href="https://github.com/confluentinc/cp-helm-charts"&gt;Confluent Platform Helm charts&lt;/a&gt; enable you to deploy Confluent Platform services on Kubernetes for development, test, and proof of concept environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-installing-charts" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#installing-charts"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Installing Charts&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;helm repo add confluentinc https://confluentinc.github.io/cp-helm-charts/
helm repo update
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-documentation" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#documentation"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Documentation&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Confluent Helm Chart documentation is located at &lt;a href="https://docs.confluent.io/current/quickstart/cp-helm-charts/docs/index.html" rel="nofollow"&gt;docs.confluent.io&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-contributing" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#contributing"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Contributing&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We welcome any contributions:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Report all enhancements, bugs, and tasks as &lt;a href="https://github.com/confluentinc/cp-helm-charts/issues"&gt;GitHub issues&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide fixes or enhancements by opening pull requests in GitHub&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-thanks" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#thanks"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Thanks&lt;/h2&gt;
